column5: Thought some of you muskie guys might find this interesting, I liked all the empirical data, in some of the articles.  http://www.musky.com/2012single/sr3.cfm
link doesnt work! err oops thanks... try this searched "weather "  http://www.musky.com/2012single/SearchPage.html

Interesting read ...however I've caught muskies all thru the day and night ..top water in a foot and half chop , full moon ..dark side..east wind .this wind that wind ..I've come to realize I have no pattern..I like fishing the new moon it " seems" to be my most productive time
